        "sender_full_name": "Chengsong Tan",
        "timestamp": 1727101371
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"233198\">Mathias Fleury</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/202961-General/topic/Isabelle.2FML.20function.20turns.20state.20mode.20to.20proof.20mode/near/471883838\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Remark that <code>insert assms</code> is useless in Isar mode</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>In my project I found it quite the contrary--sometimes insert assms would increase the probability sledgehammer finds a proof.</p>",
